{
    "title": "Alcohol",
    "screens": [
        {
            "content": [
                {
                    "type": "richtext",
                    "items": [
                        {
                            "text": "Alcoholic drinks contain ethanol, a",
                            "color": 4280690214
                        },
                        {
                            "text": " psychoactive and toxic",
                            "color": 4294923571
                        },
                        {
                            "text": " substance that can cause dependence.",
                            "color": 4280690214
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "content": [
                {
                    "type": "richtext",
                    "items": [
                        {
                            "text": "According to the WHO, there is",
                            "color": 4280690214
                        },
                        {
                            "text": " no safe dose",
                            "color": 4294923571
                        },
                        {
                            "text": " of alcohol for your health.",
                            "color": 4280690214
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "content": [
                {
                    "type": "richtext",
                    "items": [
                        {
                            "text": "Alcohol is linked to liver disease, heart disease, various cancers, and mental health issues.",
                            "color": 4280690214
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "content": [
                {
                    "type": "richtext",
                    "items": [
                        {
                            "text": "It has",
                            "color": 4280690214
                        },
                        {
                            "text": " no nutritional value",
                            "color": 4294923571
                        },
                        {
                            "text": " but contains calories.",
                            "color": 4280690214
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "content": [
                {
                    "type": "richtext",
                    "items": [
                        {
                            "text": "Alcohol",
                            "color": 4280690214
                        },
                        {
                            "text": " reduces nutrient absorption",
                            "color": 4294923571
                        },
                        {
                            "text": " and worsens metabolism, making it harder to maintain a healthy weight.",
                            "color": 4280690214
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "content": [
                {
                    "type": "richtext",
                    "items": [
                        {
                            "text": "If you decide to drink, try to",
                            "color": 4280690214
                        },
                        {
                            "text": " keep it moderate and be mindful",
                            "color": 4282888794
                        },
                        {
                            "text": " of how much you're having.",
                            "color": 4280690214
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "content": [
                {
                    "type": "richtext",
                    "items": [
                        {
                            "text": "It's usually recommended to stick to",
                            "color": 4280690214
                        },
                        {
                            "text": " 1 drink once per week:",
                            "color": 4282888794
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "type": "list",
                    "items": [
                        {
                            "type": "richtext",
                            "items": [
                                {
                                    "text": "120 ml of wine",
                                    "color": 4280690214
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "richtext",
                            "items": [
                                {
                                    "text": "300 ml of beer",
                                    "color": 4280690214
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "richtext",
                            "items": [
                                {
                                    "text": "50 ml of spirits",
                                    "color": 4280690214
                                }
                            ]
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "content": [
                {
                    "type": "richtext",
                    "items": [
                        {
                            "text": "Choose",
                            "color": 4280690214
                        },
                        {
                            "text": " natural drinks",
                            "color": 4282888794
                        },
                        {
                            "text": " like dry wine or beer, and avoid drinks with",
                            "color": 4280690214
                        },
                        {
                            "text": " sugars and artificial additives.",
                            "color": 4294923571
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "content": [
                {
                    "type": "richtext",
                    "items": [
                        {
                            "text": "Moderate drinking might be okay for some, but it's important to",
                            "color": 4280690214
                        },
                        {
                            "text": " know the risks and set your limits. ",
                            "color": 4282888794
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "content": [
                {
                    "type": "richtext",
                    "items": [
                        {
                            "text": "If you struggle with dependency,",
                            "color": 4280690214
                        },
                        {
                            "text": " seek for the help.",
                            "color": 4282888794
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        }
    ]
}